hands_on_practices.solution:
1. Stagnation enthalpy:  
$$h_{0}=h+\frac{u^{2}}{2}\quad\Rightarrow\quad u=\sqrt{2\,(h_{0}-h)}.$$
2. Isentropic relation:  
$$\frac{\rho}{\rho_{0}}=\Bigl(\frac{T}{T_{0}}\Bigr)^{\frac{1}{\gamma-1}},\quad T=\frac{h}{c_{p}},\;T_{0}=\frac{h_{0}}{c_{p}}  
\;\Rightarrow\;\rho=\rho_{0}\Bigl(\frac{h}{h_{0}}\Bigr)^{\frac{1}{\gamma-1}}.$$
3. Mass flux:  
$$G(h)=\rho\,u=\rho_{0}\Bigl(\frac{h}{h_{0}}\Bigr)^{\frac{1}{\gamma-1}}\sqrt{2\,(h_{0}-h)}.$$
4. Let $n=\frac{1}{\gamma-1}$. Then $G\propto h^{n}(h_{0}-h)^{1/2}$ and  
$$\frac{dG}{dh}=0\;\Rightarrow\;\frac{n}{h}=\frac{1}{2(h_{0}-h)}\;\Rightarrow\;h^{*}=\frac{2n}{2n+1}\,h_{0}=\frac{2}{\gamma+1}\,h_{0}.$$
5. Substitute $h^{*}$:  
$$G_{\mathrm{crit}}=\rho_{0}\Bigl(\tfrac{2}{\gamma+1}\Bigr)^{\frac{1}{\gamma-1}}
\sqrt{2\Bigl(h_{0}-\tfrac{2h_{0}}{\gamma+1}\Bigr)}
=\rho_{0}\Bigl(\tfrac{2}{\gamma+1}\Bigr)^{\frac{1}{\gamma-1}}
\sqrt{\tfrac{2(\gamma-1)}{\gamma+1}h_{0}}.$$
6. Use $\rho_{0}=\frac{P_{0}}{R\,T_{0}}$, $h_{0}=\frac{\gamma R\,T_{0}}{\gamma-1}$:  
$$G_{\mathrm{crit}}
=\frac{P_{0}}{R\,T_{0}}\Bigl(\tfrac{2}{\gamma+1}\Bigr)^{\frac{1}{\gamma-1}}
\sqrt{\tfrac{2(\gamma-1)}{\gamma+1}\,\frac{\gamma R\,T_{0}}{\gamma-1}}
=P_{0}\sqrt{\frac{\gamma}{R\,T_{0}}}\Bigl(\tfrac{2}{\gamma+1}\Bigr)^{\frac{\gamma+1}{2(\gamma-1)}}.$$
